trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> types to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: Expone los tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> a la automatización de la interfaz de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> representing the bounding rectangle of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> que representa el rectángulo delimitador del <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetBoundingRectangle" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetBoundingRectangle" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> that contains the coordinates of the element, or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Rect.Empty" /> if the element is not a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Interop.HwndSource" /> and a <see cref="T:System.Windows.PresentationSource" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> que contiene las coordenadas del elemento o <see cref="P:System.Windows.Rect.Empty" /> si el elemento no es <see cref="T:System.Windows.Interop.HwndSource" /> ni <see cref="T:System.Windows.PresentationSource" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Because <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer> provides access to its content through <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>, this method always returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Dado que <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer> proporciona acceso a su contenido a través de <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>, este método devuelve siempre `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> that represents the clickable space that is on the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> que representa el espacio interactivo que se encuentra en <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> que está asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClickablePoint" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClickablePoint" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> on the element that allows a click.
trans-unit.target: El <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> en el elemento que permite un clic.

trans-unit.source: The point values are (<see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />) if the element is not a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Interop.HwndSource" /> and a <see cref="T:System.Windows.PresentationSource" />.
trans-unit.target: Los valores de punto son (<see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />) si el elemento no es <see cref="T:System.Windows.Interop.HwndSource" /> ni <see cref="T:System.Windows.PresentationSource" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" /> is off of the screen.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TextElementAutomationPeer" /> está fuera de la pantalla.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsOffscreen" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsOffscreen" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the element is not on the screen; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el elemento no está en la pantalla; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad no indica si el elemento está visible.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, the element can be on the screen but still not be visible.
trans-unit.target: En algunas circunstancias, el elemento puede estar en la pantalla pero sigue sin ser visible.

trans-unit.source: An example is an element that is obscured by other elements.
trans-unit.target: Un ejemplo es un elemento que está oculto por otros elementos.
